        "description": "<p>Recent Products Block for WooCommerce is a block plugin by which you can showcase your WooCommerce Recently added product in block Widgets, or anywhere in the block editor area.<\/p>\n<p>Discover an innovative way to exhibit your latest WooCommerce products effortlessly with the Recent Products Block for WooCommerce. Recent Products Block seamlessly integrates with the WordPress Gutenberg editor, empowering you to showcase your most recently added products with utmost flexibility.<\/p>\n<p>Revolutionize your WooCommerce product display strategy with Recent Products Block for WooCommerce \u2013 where customization meets simplicity. With this plugin transform the way your customers explore your latest offerings!<\/p>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/bblockswp.com\/demo\/woocommerce-recent-products\/\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">Demos<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<h4>Features<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Query<\/strong>: Display the product as your query. You can show products by the stock filter, category filter etc.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Layout<\/strong>: Set different columns in different devices for responsiveness. Also, custom column and row gap.<\/li>\n<li><strong>Element Show\/Hide<\/strong>: Show or hide product elements, such as product image, title, rating, price, and add to cart button.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>How to use<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First, install the WooCommerce Recent Products plugin<\/li>\n<li>Add the WooCommerce Recent Products block from the block category called &#8220;Widgets&#8221; in the Gutenberg editor.<\/li>\n<li>You can change block settings from the right-side settings sidebar.<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>Enjoy!<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li>\n<p>For installation help click on Installation Tab<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>Feedback<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Did you like this plugin? Dislike it? Do you have a feature request? <a href=\"mailto:&#115;u&#x70;&#112;&#x6f;&#114;&#x74;&#064;&#x62;&#112;l&#x75;&#103;&#x69;&#110;&#x73;&#046;&#x63;&#x6f;&#109;\" title=\"Send feedback\"